Privacy Policy
Welcome to the
Blood Sugar Master
app! We are committed to protecting your privacy and
                personal information. Before you use our application, please be sure to read this privacy policy
                carefully to understand how we collect, use, store and protect your data. If you do not agree to any
                content of this Privacy Policy, we recommend that you do not continue to use this application.
Information Collection and Use
1.1 Collection of personal
                information:
When using the Blood Sugar
                Master application, we may collect your personal information, including but not limited to your name,
                age, gender and other identifying information. This information will be used to help us provide better
                personalized services and improve application functionality.
1.2 Collection of blood sugar
                data:
Blood Sugar Master is an application
                for recording blood sugar data, so we will collect the blood sugar data you input through the
                application, including blood sugar level, date and time, etc. The purpose of this data is to help you
                better track and manage your blood sugar levels.
1.3 Device information:
In order to optimize application performance and improve
                user experience, we may collect your device information, including mobile device type, operating system
                version and application version.
1.4 Log information:
We will automatically collect log information related to
                your usage, such as the date and time you visit the application, the functions and pages you use, IP
                address, device event information, etc. These log information will help us analyze and solve potential
                problems to improve the stability and security of the application.
Purpose of information use
2.1 Provision of services:
The personal information and blood sugar data collected
                by us will be used to provide functions and services of the Blood Sugar Master application. This
                includes recording and tracking your blood sugar data to help you monitor and manage your blood sugar
                levels.
2.2 Data analysis:
We may anonymize and summarize the collected blood
                glucose data for application function improvement and performance optimization. These statistical
                information will help us better understand user needs and usage habits.
2.3 Notifications and
                communication:
We may send you updates,
                notifications or other information related to the application, including but not limited to the launch
                of new functions, event invitations, technical support and security tips, etc. These notifications and
                information are critical to keep the application running properly and improve the user
                experience.
2.4 Legal requirements:
In some cases, we may use or disclose your personal
                information in accordance with applicable laws and regulations, court orders or government department
                requirements.
Information Storage and Protection
We will take reasonable security measures to protect the
                personal information you provide from unauthorized access, use or disclosure. The security measures we
                use include but are not limited to encryption technology, access control measures and Secure Sockets
                Layer (SSL) technology to protect your personal information.
Although we take reasonable security measures, please note
                that due to the nature of the Internet, we cannot guarantee the absolute security of your information
                while in transit.
