Our Apps may contain links to third-party websites or
                services. This Privacy Policy applies only to our app, and we have no control over the privacy practices
                of other websites or services. We strongly encourage you to review the privacy policies of websites you
                visit after you leave our application to understand their information collection and use
                practices.
Analytics
We may use third-party Service providers to monitor and
                analyze the use of our Service.
•
Google Analytics
Google Analytics is a web analytics service offered by
                Google that tracks and reports website traffic. Google uses the data collected to track and monitor the
                use of our Service. This data is shared with other Google services. Google may use the collected data to
                contextualise and personalise the ads of its own advertising network.
Advertising
We may use Service providers to show advertisements to You
                to help support and maintain Our Service.
•
Google AdSense
Google, as a third party vendor, uses cookies to serve ads
                on our Service. Google's use of the DoubleClick cookie enables it and its partners to serve ads to our
                users based on their visit to our Service or other websites on the Internet.
•
AdMob by Google
AdMob by Google is provided by Google Inc.
Changes to the Privacy Policy
From time to time, we may update this Privacy Policy to
                reflect improvements to the App and user feedback. The updated Privacy Policy will be posted on our app
                and the date of change will be updated to the latest date. We encourage you to review this Privacy
                Policy periodically to understand how any changes affect you.
Minors' Privacy Protection
We do not knowingly collect personal information from
                minors under the age of 13. If you are a minor under the age of 13, please do not provide us with any
                personal information. If you are a parent or guardian and find that your child has provided us with
                personal information, please contact us and we will delete the relevant information as soon as
                possible.
Contact Us
If you have any questions, comments or concerns about our
                privacy policy, please get in touch with us via the contact form within the app. Thank you for trusting
                and using the Blood Sugar Master app!